1) cat 1 2 | sort | uniq
2) cat 1 2 | sort | uniq -d
3) cat 1 2 | sort | uniq -u

kavonm@2013:~$ cat 1
123
456
kavonm@2013:~$ cat 2
456
kavonm@2013:~$ cat 1 2
123
456
456
kavonm@2013:~$ cat 1 2 | sort | uniq
123
456
kavonm@2013:~$ cat 1 2 | sort | uniq -d
456
kavonm@2013:~$ cat 1 2 | sort | uniq -u
123
 
